platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: A story of beauty and illusion
一段讓你置身美麗幻境的故事

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 母女情為幾何解謎注入深度
新ステージ「失われた森」が追加
母女情讓幾何解謎更有溫度

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We couldn’t wait to go back to the land of twisty towers and uncanny beauty—and this sequel didn’t let us down. With its striking colors and level design, it’s even more stunning than the first game. New elements like light beams and controlling two characters make the puzzles even trickier. The bond between that mother and child is what we’ll remember most, though—their relationship moved us in a way few games do.
如果你迫不及待想再次回到旋轉扭曲的建築群中，那麼《紀念碑谷 2》一定不會讓你失望。它在顏色運用與關卡設計上更勝前作，除了加入光束等新元素外，還增加了一次控制兩個角色的玩法，使得闖關過程變得更具挑戰性。遊戲中母親與孩子間的溫情互動更是獨一無二、觸動人心。

We couldn’t wait to go back to the land of twisty towers and uncanny beauty—and this sequel didn’t let us down. With its striking colours and level design, it’s even more stunning than the first game. New elements like light beams and controlling two characters make the puzzles even trickier. The bond between that mother and child is what we’ll remember most, though—their relationship moved us in a way few games do.
如果你迫不及待想再次回到旋轉扭曲的建築群中，那麼《紀念碑谷 2》一定不會讓你失望。它在顏色的運用與關卡的設計上更勝前作，除了加入光束等新元素外，還增加了一次控制兩個角色的玩法，使得闖關過程變得更具挑戰性。遊戲中母親與孩子間的溫情互動更是獨一無二、觸動人心。

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: A powerful bond between mother and child drives this gorgeous, unforgettable game.
An unforgettable adventure full of challenging puzzles and gorgeous visuals.
